body:

### Goals

- Give teachers tools to create lessons for NJSLS climate standards.
- Review lessons Sparkle Labs has created that are applicable to the climate standards.
- Teach the use and application of the *Watt Meter.*
- Create a structured design workshop environment to allow the teachers to work together on the climate standards.

[NJSLS : Climate Change : 6-8](njsls-climate-change-grades-6-8)

